setFormDir 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set group formation heading. Accepted heading range is 0 to 360. Formation 
 is facing this direction unless enemy is seen. When group is moving 
, this value is overriden by movement direction.  
Syntax:  
 group setFormDir heading 
Parameters: 
group: Object or Group 
heading: Number 
Return Value: 
 Nothing